org.apache.hadoop.hbase.wal

Class OutputSink

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.wal.OutputSink
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractRecoveredEditsOutputSink, BoundedRecoveredHFilesOutputSink

    @InterfaceAudience.Private
abstract class OutputSink
extends Object
    The following class is an abstraction class to provide a common interface to support different ways of consuming recovered edits.
